source /opt/ros/indigo/setup.bash
source ~/catkin-ws/devel/setup.bash

catkin_init_workspace: initialize the workspace (obviously);
catkin_create_pkg: create a new package (with dependencies);
catkin_make: convenience alternative tool for cmake;

rospack find [package-name]: find a package by its name (after sourcing);
rospack depends1 [package-name]: list dependencies;
rospack depend [package-name]: list dependencies recursively. 
roscd: change directory directly to a package or a stack;
rosls: ls directly in a package by name; 
rosout: ros equivalent of stdout/stderr.
roscore: master + rosout + parameter server.
rosnode list: displays information about the ros nodes that are currently running. 
rosnode ping [package-name]: test whether a package is up. 
rosrun [package-name] [node-name]
rostopic echo [data]:
rostopic type [topic]:
rostopic pub [topic] [message-type] [args]
rostopic hz: report the rate at which data is published;
rosmsg show [message-type]:
rosservice list: list the services provided by some node;
rosservice type: argument type;
rosservice call: call a service;
rosparam list: list the parameters of some node;
rosparam set [param-name]: set a parameter;
rosparam get [param-name]: get a parameter.
rosparam dump [file-name];
rosparam load [file-name];
roslaunch [package] [filename.launch];
rosed [package-name] [filename]: edit a file within a package. 
roscp [package-name] [file-to-copy-path] [copy-path]; 
rossrv show <service-type>;
rosmsg show <message-type>;
rosbag record -a;
rosbag info <bagfile>;
rosbag play <bagfile>;
rosbag wtf.

: packages = CMakeList.txt + package.xml;
: package.xml = ...;
: package.xml + message_generation/runtime.

node: an executable that uses ros to communicate with other nodes.
messages: ros data type used when subscribing or publishing to a topic.
topics: nodes can publish messages to a topic as well as
  subscribe to a topic to receive messages.
master: name service for ros.
publisher;
subscriber;
service;
client.

: rosrun rqt_graph rqt_graph: the information exchange network;
: rosrun rqt_plot rqt_plot: the data plot;
: rosrun rqt_console rqt_console: the data logger;
: rosrun rqt_logger_level rqt_logger_level: the data logger level changer.

msg: describes the fields of a ros message.
srv: describes a service. 

rosrun rviz rviz
roslaunch drcsim_gazebo atlas.launch

